[05Ch 0092   8]                   Write Mask : 0000000000000001
[064h 0100   4]              Command Latency : 00000FA0
[068h 0104   4]          Maximum Access Rate : 0000EA60
[06Ch 0108   2]      Minimum Turnaround Time : 0000

